ef":"Ps.72.1","text":"Give the king thy judgments, O God, and thy righteousness unto the king’s son."},{"id":"recdz1GLeh4Jsp7ti","ref":"Ps.72.2","text":"He shall judge thy people with righteousness, and thy poor with judgment."},{"id":"recBi3jh2Nb5beGG4","ref":"Ps.72.3","text":"The mountains shall bring peace to the people, and the little hills, by righteousness."},{"id":"rec4IUmpljximMQgh","ref":"Ps.72.4","text":"He shall judge the poor of the people, he shall save the children of the needy, and shall break in pieces the oppressor."},{"id":"recBq1yEbcHWmY6BR","ref":"Ps.72.5","text":"They shall fear thee as long as the sun and moon endure, throughout all generations."},{"id":"recFaMBZKeCQUxjTO","ref":"Ps.72.6","text":"He shall come down like rain upon the mown grass: as showers that water the earth."},{"id":"rec1A7CtgExFYRYH5","ref":"Ps.72.7","text":"In his days shall the righteous flourish; and abundance of peace so long as the moon endureth."},{"id":"recAel4fSxYsiHjk5","ref":"Ps.72.8","text":"He shall have dominion also from sea to sea, and from the river unto the ends of the earth."}]}
